Package: bicon
Type: Package
Title: Bivariate modelling using the conditional approach
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2015-02-27
Authors@R: c(person("Andrew", "Zammit-Mangion", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "andrewzm@gmail.com"))
